Added GetAttribute (equivalent to SetAttribute).
Change GetLowStop and GetHighStop to return joint limits.  If you want to get ode dHiStop* or dLoStop* params, use GetAttribute("hi_stop", [index]) or GetAttribute("lo_stop", [index]).
Update simulated cfm damping to recover original cfm and erp when joint limit is violated.
